text: Wave goes, wave runs. This thousand miles strong waves runs forever, washing off.
Things of world mix with wave and wave goes on. It's happy, it's sad. We can't distinguish these in the wave.
Success or failures in the wave we can't see there is or not.
Love you, hate you. Do you know? Like river is go can't stop.
Turn thousand around, turn thousand beaches. We can't also stop fight inside.
Happy again, sad again. Even don't know how smile and cry.
Still want turn so many waves, up and down enough in my heart.
